  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the effectiveness of adding Seeking Safety to
      standard substance abuse treatment to adding a control condition: Women's Health Education to
      standard substance abuse treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
